---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Notre Equipe" lang="fr" description="Rencontrez l'equipe devouee de Forest International School Paris - des educateurs passionnes qui accompagnent les enfants dans un environnement d'apprentissage en pleine nature.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-20 lg:py-28 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2d5a3d] to-[#1e3d29]">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=\"60\" height=\"60\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"%3E%3Cg fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"%3E%3Cg fill=\"%23ffffff\" fill-opacity=\"0.1\"%3E%3Cpath d=\"M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z\"/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E')]"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962]/20 rounded-full text-[#c9a962] font-semibold text-sm mb-6 border border-[#c9a962]/30">
        Nos Collaborateurs
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Notre Equipe
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Des educateurs devoues qui accompagnent les enfants dans un environnement d'apprentissage en pleine nature et d'excellence academique.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Leadership Team Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-[#faf8f5]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] font-semibold text-sm mb-4">Direction de l'Ecole</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29] mb-4">Equipe de Direction</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          L'equipe de direction guidant Forest International School vers l'excellence educative.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Sophie Lovejoy -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-36 h-36 lg:w-44 lg:h-44">
            <img
              src="/images/team/sophie-lovejoy.avif"
              alt="Sophie Lovejoy"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-xl">Sophie Lovejoy</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962]/20 rounded-full text-[#c9a962] text-sm mt-2 font-semibold">Directrice</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Matthew Jackson -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-36 h-36 lg:w-44 lg:h-44">
            <img
              src="/images/team/matthew-jackson.avif"
              alt="Matthew Jackson"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-xl">Matthew Jackson</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962]/20 rounded-full text-[#c9a962] text-sm mt-2 font-semibold">Directeur Pedagogique</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Mr. Vlad Krolka -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-36 h-36 lg:w-44 lg:h-44">
            <img
              src="/images/team/mr-kralka.avif"
              alt="Mr. Vlad Krolka"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-xl">Mr. Vlad Krolka</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962]/20 rounded-full text-[#c9a962] text-sm mt-2 font-semibold">Enseignant STEM</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Ms. Sharon D'Amico -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-36 h-36 lg:w-44 lg:h-44">
            <img
              src="/images/team/miss-sharon.avif"
              alt="Ms. Sharon D'Amico"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-xl">Ms. Sharon D'Amico</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962]/20 rounded-full text-[#c9a962] text-sm mt-2 font-semibold">Responsable Litteratie</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Teaching Team Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] font-semibold text-sm mb-4">Nos Educateurs</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29] mb-4">Equipe Pedagogique</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Des educateurs passionnes engages a developper le potentiel de chaque enfant a travers l'apprentissage en pleine nature.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Teaching Team Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
        <!-- Mr. Vlad Krolka -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-28 h-28 lg:w-32 lg:h-32">
            <img
              src="/images/team/mr-kralka.avif"
              alt="Mr. Vlad Krolka"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-base lg:text-lg">Mr. Vlad Krolka</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] text-xs lg:text-sm mt-2">Enseignant STEM</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Ms. Sharon D'Amico -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-28 h-28 lg:w-32 lg:h-32">
            <img
              src="/images/team/miss-sharon.avif"
              alt="Ms. Sharon D'Amico"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-base lg:text-lg">Ms. Sharon D'Amico</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] text-xs lg:text-sm mt-2">Responsable Litteratie</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Ms. Ruta -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-28 h-28 lg:w-32 lg:h-32">
            <img
              src="/images/team/miss-ruta.avif"
              alt="Ms. Ruta"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-base lg:text-lg">Ms. Ruta</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] text-xs lg:text-sm mt-2">Referente Besoins Speciaux</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Ms. Hannah -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-28 h-28 lg:w-32 lg:h-32">
            <img
              src="/images/team/miss-hannah.avif"
              alt="Ms. Hannah"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-base lg:text-lg">Ms. Hannah</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] text-xs lg:text-sm mt-2">Enseignante</span>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1">Responsable Maternelle</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Ms. Mary -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-28 h-28 lg:w-32 lg:h-32">
            <img
              src="/images/team/miss-marie.avif"
              alt="Ms. Mary"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-base lg:text-lg">Ms. Mary</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] text-xs lg:text-sm mt-2">Enseignante</span>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1">Responsable Francais</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Ms. Chloe -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-28 h-28 lg:w-32 lg:h-32">
            <img
              src="/images/team/miss-chloe.avif"
              alt="Ms. Chloe"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-base lg:text-lg">Ms. Chloe</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] text-xs lg:text-sm mt-2">Enseignante</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Ms. Delphin -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-28 h-28 lg:w-32 lg:h-32">
            <img
              src="/images/team/miss-daulphine.avif"
              alt="Ms. Delphin"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-base lg:text-lg">Ms. Delphin</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] text-xs lg:text-sm mt-2">Assistante Pedagogique</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Mr Elliot -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-28 h-28 lg:w-32 lg:h-32">
            <img
              src="/images/team/mr-elliot.avif"
              alt="Mr Elliot"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-base lg:text-lg">Mr Elliot</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] text-xs lg:text-sm mt-2">Assistant Pedagogique</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Susanna -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-28 h-28 lg:w-32 lg:h-32">
            <img
              src="/images/team/susanne-shamir.avif"
              alt="Susanna"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-base lg:text-lg">Susanna</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] text-xs lg:text-sm mt-2">Assistante de Direction</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Christophe -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-28 h-28 lg:w-32 lg:h-32">
            <img
              src="/images/team/jean-christophe.avif"
              alt="Christophe"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-base lg:text-lg">Christophe</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] text-xs lg:text-sm mt-2">Maitre-nageur</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/images/promo-2023.jpg"
        alt="Forest International School"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-10"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29] mb-6">Rejoignez Notre Communaute</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Decouvrez la chaleur et le devouement de notre equipe en personne. Planifiez une visite pour voir comment nous developpons le potentiel de chaque enfant.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/fr/admissions" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-[#2d5a3d] text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-[#1e3d29] transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
          Commencer Votre Candidature
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/fr/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-[#2d5a3d] font-bold rounded-full border-2 border-[#2d5a3d] hover:bg-[#2d5a3d] hover:text-white transition-colors shadow-lg">
          Planifier une Visite
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
